                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870912-103-defend969 t17870912-103-punish494"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice GROSE.</p>
